{
  "stem": "10587.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We also-- it was written in the papers as well as-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and we were concerned about it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember my father talking about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But they felt that, you know, being who they are and where they are, that maybe nothing would happen to them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was a big mistake.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That-- because I remember when they were talking about these things and-- and even I-- I used to read the papers quite a bit, whatever paper we had in Oswiecim, because I was fascinated prior to that how, for so many years, the Japanese and the Chinese were fighting, you know, and so many people were killed.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All this was taking place, and the Poles in the parliament were talking about the shechita.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if you-- the [HEBREW] means how you slaughter animal, like for food, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they did not-- they were discussing it that the Jews should not-- you cannot shoot the animal.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It has to be slaughtered by a shochet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what they were occupied with.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because not too long after that, I was listening to the radio where they were-- where the Germans were getting ready to occupy Poland.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And to-- listening to the radio was like a comedy, that they had [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] passwords like [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we could see-- they had little tanks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We could see the tanks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were totally disorganized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the horses pulling the-- the-- the cannons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they mainly, the little tanks, like maybe one or two man tank, probably one man tank.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when they would say [POLISH], they would go one direction.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When they would say [POLISH], they would say-- go in the other direction.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
